{"tid":2133944,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"(野餐卡) 3hk係豐澤出左張$88 365日年卡 有110GB 42M速數據 1萬分鐘 通宵時間任用數據","createTime":"2020-07-31T11:19:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-04T07:20:19.000Z","uid":252492,"like":2,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"a3e809b38393f5ff54ea029737f49945981edc21","tid":2133944,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T11:19:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/3146/216345/1/?fbclid=IwAR0aQ3ln_LI9s6jdYZ-kHcEiQX49I1h1RPhQvlAKuon4e6JJ7kJ8YMG20HM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F3146%2F216345%2F1%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0aQ3ln_LI9s6jdYZ-kHcEiQX49I1h1RPhQvlAKuon4e6JJ7kJ8YMG20HM&d=LJfbHi1nzQR09hbgKwAG1yHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=8e67fa05\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/3146/216345/1/?fbclid=IwAR0aQ3ln_LI9s6jdYZ-kHcEiQX49I1h1RPhQvlAKuon4e6JJ7kJ8YMG20HM</a><br />\n<br />\n$88 有 110GB 42M 數據 + 10000 通話分鐘<br />\n豐澤獨家推出全新年卡，張卡個名叫 ChaTime，賣價 $88，包 110GB 數據，有效期為 395 日，網絡速度最高為 42Mbps，而通宵時段 (即 23:00 - 07:00)，更可以無限任上，看上去好平，畢竟市面其他有 100GB 以上的儲值卡，都起碼要 $200。而家 $88 買到，有無伏，點解會那麼便宜？<br />\n<br />\n原因是，它的 110GB 數據，其實是有用途限制，留意細則，原來本地數據用量只有 10GB，其餘 100GB 都是社交媒體數據，即是用到 Facebook (包括 Facebook Messenger 以及手機網頁版)、Instagram、WhatsApp、Line 以及 WeChat。100GB 社交媒體數據，理論上好難用得完，除非你經常在 Facebook 看直播，或者 WhatsApp 同人視像通話吧。<br />\n<br />\n不過值得一提的是，一般年卡例如 3HK 自己張萬能卡，通話分鐘都是只有 2000 分鐘，而這張 ChaTime 儲值卡，卻能提供 10000 本地通話分鐘，生意人就算不用來上網，當是一張打電話用的 SIM，都是一個不錯選擇。"},{"pid":"70064dee7ac15081d6858871dfcef8687e038777","tid":2133944,"uid":11521,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T11:24:13.000Z","msg":"唔可以MNP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45bdcf174b7ac08cc918e27ef5dec3d90859bd27","tid":2133944,"uid":78304,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T11:27:35.000Z","msg":"萬年卡好過啦"},{"pid":"ce2ab690fb8a7bec75f5564d2b72bf3f9da536b0","tid":2133944,"uid":201374,"like":32,"d